，一日唔使就連片都刪埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdbe9c3fe4f2842a83c4612eb1c4f03c3e35128","tid":1974264,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5760e8791b4803c500eb970a1587b40cc1d9461","tid":1974264,"uid":42411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91c964d30432af2a6827bb2115ce5980f2077f82","tid":1974264,"uid":6435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"07efbe8f0a1400b1072524a0d462efb590615b07","tid":1974264,"uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"Dcard 台灣發起先，當然台灣人用多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:40:41.000Z","msg":"本身台灣網<br />\n香港人無啦啦點會走去用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T17:45:32.000Z","msg":"仲要Dcard一堆on9屁孩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T18:04:02.000Z","msg":"咁同連登差唔多啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1058907715e5a6239e1632f1e0ee7a989b1045","tid":1974264,"uid":82450,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T18:04:43.000Z","msg":"阿滴今次引咗好多台豬出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩充大頭仔、籌款發達、綠營內鬥，希望唔會變成台灣版藍絲大聯盟"},{"pid":"c3c48f63ca5c4756a0ebb85b2f22ef2f7463d912","tid":1974264,"uid":255816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T19:09:53.000Z","msg":"佢真係良心youtuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持"},{"pid":"ce7ea84ff359a4fe74350043fd020a34934b480f","tid":1974264,"uid":217080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T19:23:02.000Z","msg":"Dcard好撚多五毛/on9話呀滴借廣告上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一佢本身已經好紅，其次佢得罪中共唔會開拓到新客源（教華人英文），咁都話佢想上位想曬